<h1>New: The Pokayoke Guide to Developing Software</h1>

<p>I&#8217;ve put together a new guide for developing software, from idea to architectural details. The idea was to combine all the good ideas I&#8217;d heard from various areas of software development into a single, concise document. I&#8217;ve also added some new stuff &#8212; I think my need/idea model is actually a pretty good way to generate startup (and other) ideas.</p>

<p><a href="http://pokayokeguide.com/">The Pokayoke Guide to Developing Software</a></p>

<p>I&#8217;m eager for suggestions and feedback.</p>


<p><i>You should follow me on twitter <a href="http://twitter.com/aaronsw">here</a>.</i></p>
<p class="posted">June 26, 2012</p>

